data.text:
@andreconfiado Hello André,
the counters opens 3 hours before departure.
Best regards, Alessandra

@BeingJustHonest Hallo,
ich kann deine Verärgerung zwar verstehen, allerdings haben wir hier auf Twitter keinen Zugriff auf die Gepäcksysteme und können daher in diesem Fall leider nicht weiterhelfen. Bitte bleibe in Kontakt mit dem zuständigen Team von Lost &amp; Found.
 Viele Grüße, Alessandra

@samanthadowden Hi there, 
We are sorry for the inconvenience. We have replied to your PM, please check your inbox.
Best regards, Shawn

@cathulu26 [2/2] Please check the following link 
https://t.co/sbRZzqs60x - it gives you an overview of information about additional baggage and links you to the option of purchasing one online via your booking code. 
Best regards, Shawn

@dearcheco Hello Judith,
we are currently experiencing an unusual increase in volume. We want you to know that this is not typical for the type of service we strive to provide our customers. You can send us your booking code in a DM, we'll try to help. 
Best regards, Alessandra

@MrsEntwistle Dear Samantha,
sorry to hear you're still waiting. We kindly ask you for some more patience. Our colleagues are doing their best.
Best regards, Alessandra

@Qozmozs @MrsEntwistle Dear Edwin,
you can check the status of your baggage online via this link https://t.co/hrzpeJ2rHC 
Best regards, Alessandra

@c_kronenberg [1/2]
Hallo Christopher, 
Es tut uns leid, dass Sie Schwierigkeiten hatten telefonisch mit uns in Kontakt zu treten. Aufgrund der aktuellen Situation sind leider alle unsere Kanäle überlastet und es kann zu längeren Wartezeiten kommen.

@mlestew Hi there, 
We are sorry for all the trouble caused due to the flight irregularity. Please send us your booking code, so we can take a closer look. Many thanks for your patience and understanding. 
Best regards, Shawn

@sty0pa Hi there, 
Please be so kind and send us your claim via the following link https://t.co/1jYyfcuAde
Best regards, Shawn
